Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:05.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.76,0:00:08.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:09.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:14.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,After a quick bit of fan service,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:16.92,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,we begin with a summary of the last episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:21.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Accompanied by his maid, \Na mysterious boy has come to see Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:24.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,What might his true identity be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This boy is Wataru Tachibana
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he is Nagi's... betrothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.07,0:00:37.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all. End of summary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya gotta get over yer bashfulness!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya can't win scenes for yerself like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. What yer character \Nlacks is punch, Mr. Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The comedic drive to step forward, \Neven if ya hafta push people aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my glasses, my glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:01:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My glasses, my glasses, \Nmy glasses, my glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.21,0:01:04.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:08.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who waits upon others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.81,0:01:11.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is a formal guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:14.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who is there to support his \Nmistress in all aspects of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:16.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:20.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This is about a boy who fights \Nand puts his life on the line for a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:24.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A super combat battle story!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I get more screen time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:37.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi ni kaketa bokura no yukue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:37.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination that we've \Nstaked upon this earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:44.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuki-nukeru hayate no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:44.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sudden gale that cuts across
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:47.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Unmei ni makete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:47.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving in to fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:52.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shagami-komu nante tsumannai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:52.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And hunkering down is no fun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:56.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore ja kakko warui yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:56.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:01:59.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uso kara deta makoto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:01:59.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Many a true word is spoken in jest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:05.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Koukai wa kitto mi kara deta sabi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:05.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Regret is probably reaping what you sowed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:08.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zettai, nase ba naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:08.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Where there's a will, \Nthere's definitely a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:15.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ooki na hamon ni nomi-komareteku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:15.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As a great rippling wave swallows us up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:21.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Karada nami ni makasereba
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:21.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it take you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:24.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kanchigai no yume
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:24.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams that are misguided
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:28.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mato-hazure no kitai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:28.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopes that are way off base
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:33.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuyoku omoeba itsuka tsukameru sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:33.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll grab them someday, \Nif you just have conviction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:40.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi keri-age hashiri-dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:40.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick up the earth and start running
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:47.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimama ni mau kaze no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:47.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the capricious breeze that dances about
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Man's Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, betrothed, as in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a husband-to-be \Ndetermined by her parents...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that makes him her fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miss, I had no idea you had \Nan official boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're wrong! Don't misunderstand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not my boyfriend, \Nbut my betrothed! My betrothed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's something \Nour families decided on their own,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, really, I'm so surprised \Nthat you're betrothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A young lady of the upper class \Ncertainly has it different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To Nagi, his smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never told me you were betrothed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was our relationship just a game to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:44.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...apparently looked like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:47.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate's pretty angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I must resolve the \Nmisunderstanding, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But are they sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Miss marries into his family,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,won't that be the end of the Sanzenin name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no problem in that regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:03:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Nagi will not be the one \Nto marry into his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so the Miss will receive Wataru \Ninto the family as her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'm being received \Nas Nagi's husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But such a thing does not happen often.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An opportunity to marry \Nan adorable girl like Miss Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! A selfish, spoiled, \Nirresponsible manga nerd,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who thinks she's the boss of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like anyone would want her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'm taking that \Nfrom a brat like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you stupid, stupid, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my like, you ugly, ugly, ugly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I guess people who are \Nbetrothed really do get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugly! Ugly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:37.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Stupid! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that looks like they're \Ngetting along to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should go see an eye \Ndoctor or brain surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you! Can't you be \Nat least a little more ladylike?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That voice... Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... uh... Isumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:05:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be because you also heard \Nthat Nagi had a new butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I myself was of a similar mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:06.91,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,I Myself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:06.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"I myself"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I just heard some loud noises...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you were \Nfighting with Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not at all! We would never fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi and I always get along famously!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the drastic \Nchange in his persona?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that Wataru likes Isumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He likes someone else \Nwhen he's betrothed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not a betrothal \Nthat they wanted for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, does the Miss want to \Nbreak off her betrothal to Wataru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if we could marry when \Nwe don't even like each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Isumi comes to like Wataru, \Nit would solve everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but regrettably, Wataru doesn't \Nregister on Isumi's radar at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, whatever the case, \Nif Wataru and Isumi become an item,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the betrothal will be off, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It seems you finally understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, we haven't eaten this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:05:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nso how about some breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you prefer \Na Japanese breakfast, Isumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, whichever you prefer, \Nmy dear Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:13.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isumi! Don't tell me \Nyou have feelings for him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then everyone, please head \Ntowards the dining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Nagi's new butler, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:28.90,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,RROOAARR
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes, my name is Hayate Ayasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're here, how about \Na little duel before breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is it the norm for the rich and \Nfamous to have duels in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he probably wants to \Nshow off how cool he is to Isumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if he loses really badly, \Nhe may gain Isumi's sympathy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so beat the crap out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, ready to meet your fate, \Nyou stupid butler?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll warn you, though. Hayate's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he can catch up \Nto a car on a bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:09.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way a poor-looking \Nguy like him is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any experience with sabers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's about \Nthe best I can do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Once a man's decided to do something,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:30.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:33.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what the Miss asked me to do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:34.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:38.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can neatly bring the two of them \Nto an understanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi, be with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I will marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! The betrothal's off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it's settled then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch this, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:06.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate Ayasaki's greatest \Nperformance of his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:10.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:14.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Sharp instruments are dangerous, \Nso let's still get that out of the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, he got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:27.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That should've set the flag \Nfor a happy ending...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my dear Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you would lose on purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so as not to hurt the pride \Nof the violent and weak Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How kind of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru is truly strong \Nand I didn't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... never... letting you \Nget away with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat you for sure someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember this! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This wasn't how it was supposed to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness. To think he psychologically \Nbeat the crap out of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate really is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:12.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, that cheap performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:15.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he still angry that I didn't \Ntell him that I was betrothed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:20.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru has left the estate by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:23.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, as for his maid's bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water was quite fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:31.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,She was in there so long, \Nthe first half has already ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me you love me. \N({\i1}A{\i0}ishiteiru to itte ku{\i1}re{\i0})
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love beam! ({\i1}Re{\i0}nai bii{\i1}mu{\i0})
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still think it would be better \Nif I went to apologize to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I did to Wataru was inexcusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, certainly,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do feel a little sorry for him \Nto leave things like this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it, leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, for a boy \Nto cry in front of others...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How weak could he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, that is awful! Calling him weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the truth, but since he made \NWataru cry, he should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who made him cry, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So, given that I am going to apologize,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where will I be able to \Nfind Wataru's estate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Isn't that more \Nof a building than an estate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because Wataru lives
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the top of the Tachibana \NGroup's Shinjuku Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, he's in the middle of downtown?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the roads will be congested \Nat this hour in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose taking the train \Nwould be faster than driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did I say something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The train... Isumi, have you \Never been on one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have ridden the Orient Express \Nand the Siberian Express, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not any in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there aren't all \Nthat many trains running, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a game. A game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you have \Nnever ridden a train, Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But were there that many \Nbullet train stations in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! The bullet train?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! By train, you weren't \Nreferring to the bullet train?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse my abrupt question,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but do you ladies know what the "subway" is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The subway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, like the Oedo Line \Nor the Marunouchi Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are trains that run underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:22.66,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(486,21)}Murmur
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there are bullet trains \Nrunning underground in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there are trains other \Nthan bullet trains!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, underground, what kind \Nof scenery do you see outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there is nothing to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they're only \Nfor transporting Koubu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and ordinary people couldn't ride them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just during the Taisho era!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no intention \Nof going to Wataru's place,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd like to take a ride \Non this so-called subway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we are going to ride \Nthis subway thing, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:54.73,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(579,203)}Sanzenin
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But will it be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting on such a strange vehicle \Nwith just the children...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At Shinjuku Station alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:12:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,approximately 570,000 people get \Non this strange vehicle every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:07.41,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(205,287)}*Research by Hayate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, the breakdown of that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:04.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,...230,000 people \Non the Metro Shinjuku Line,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,100,000 people on the Oedo Line,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:07.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,and 240,000 people on the Marunouchi Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all for the explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're so knowledgeable, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see that? Nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we may get to see \Nsubterranean people or living dinosaurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That is why I'm saying it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, we have Isumi along with us also,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I will escort them carefully \Nto keep from getting lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of Isumi, \Nwhere in the world is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could she have gotten lost already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! We only looked away \Nfor just a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I underestimated Isumi's abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To start with, Maria, contact security.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate and I will search nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait, Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Isumi probably headed \Nfor that so-called subway, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible! There are numerous \Nsubway stations in Tokyo alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:13:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the "subway" in this case \Nis Isumi's idea of the "subway".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'd give it a 90 chance that \Nshe hasn't made it to the real subway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:03.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rum raisin! Triple on a regular cone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Isumi never makes it \Nto her destination on her own!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there will be no mistake \Nif you follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where Isumi has gone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be the closest place around \Nthat resembles the subway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, no, no, no. \NWhere in the world are we, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, I found a construction guy \Nwho sounded like he'd seen Isumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:33.54,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(320,324)}A While Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:33.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is this the entrance to the subway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The subway, where they transport \Ndinosaurs using bullet trains...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh sure, it's definitely underground, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there are all kinds of unknown \Nworlds sprawled under Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that even the government \Ndoesn't know everything about,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you just might find...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, huh?! Missy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I bought out the construction site \Nand we went underground with security.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that part went fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's a Griffon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trick of the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Part of me almost wishes it was \Nand part of me doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we should go back for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or we'll get lost for real, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You fool! Don't change \Ndirections so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were leaving me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't handle dark places \Nlike this too well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please don't make any sudden moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what do you do at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might you have trouble \Nsleeping alone at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait... it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not as if I can't sleep alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a child, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have a hard time \Nfalling asleep sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if there's a power outage, \Nit gets pitch dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's kind of dangerous, \Nyou know... like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cuter when you \Nhave qualities like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was a bit of a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, you shouldn't yell \Nin underground spaces like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you yell, they get scared \Nand come leaping out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! Let's run together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry, they'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are making a bit of a ruckus...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.25,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, how smart you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, our dreams of the subway were crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinosaurs? Subterranean men?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like they exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me. The subway \Nactually leads to Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Brazil?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. That place is on \Nthe other side of Japan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it connects us to 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only thing ya gotta be careful of is \Nthat Brazil's a foreign country, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, ya gotta show yer passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time ya have occasion \Nto ride the subway,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,show yer passport to the station staff
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and say, "One child's ticket \Nto Rio de Janeiro please."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Sakuya. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, if you're still going to \Ninsist on apologizing to Wataru,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to give this to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't open it on your \Nway there, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since there's no knowing \Nwho may be watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something to get rid \Nof her betrothed, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a bomb or something...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? If it isn't the Sanzenin family butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fancy meeting you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you come to see the Young Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, just dropping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I'm delivering \Nsomething from the Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I shall show you the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really? Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, our headquarters is this way, \Nso please be sure to follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:37.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, \Nbut is Saki avoiding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Saki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... the?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pardon me! Um, it's not \Nthat I'm avoiding you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, um, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never been held like \Nthat by a man before,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I sort of end up shying away by reflex...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I don't mean you! \NI mean men in general!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to people hating me anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... uh... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here. This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:15.53,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Video Rental Video Tachibana
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, isn't this a video rental store?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir, I have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Saki, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I brought this to you from the Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the videos that I lent Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Videos?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is the Entertainment \NDivision of the Tachibana Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinjuku flagship store \Nof Rental Video Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tachibana Group itself
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is almost dead due to \Nthe recent economic downturn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This rental store chain \Nis their last holdout now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saki, don't say such unnecessary things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the fact you're betrothed is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it means my parents \Nare counting on Nagi's family fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're used to being wealthy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they're scared of no \Nlonger having a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But where's the point in thinking \Nabout things so negatively?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make this store huge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and amass a fortune that'll \Ndwarf the Sanzenin family!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'm being taken \Ninto the family as a husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, I'm sure Isumi will also...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:30.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This boy has a foul mouth, \Nbut he's a really good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can't just let him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saki, don't just stand there! Get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rental video... So, is what \NI just delivered also...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, our goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as rich as the Miss is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surely she could just buy it \Ninstead of bothering to rent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're some extra-rare titles in \Nthis world that aren't on the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, are those DVDs also...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is Gurren Lag...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:03.05,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bamboo! Bamboo poles!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you see, we've got \Na collection of treasures
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that we can't mention out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The genres are anime \Nand special effects, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But isn't it illegal to rent them out \Nin exchange for payment?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. I'm only showing \Noff to Nagi privately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:19.15,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,207)}Wataru Only
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But someday, I'm going to surpass her \Nwith the power of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm really sorry about the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By way of apology, please allow me \Nto become a member of this store.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a customer's a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasaki, was it? I'll waive the sign-up fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already registered as a member.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I've never joined \Na rental membership before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this photo's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shun Ayasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The name's different...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.19,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(131,98)}Name
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.19,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(308,94)}Shun Ayasaki
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.19,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(132,160)}Legal Domicile
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.19,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,160)}Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.19,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(132,223)}Address
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.19,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(282,223)}Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.19,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(128,284)}Issued
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.19,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(342,285)}June 2, Heisei Year 17
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a total of 158 videos \Nthat haven't been returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At 200 yen per video per day...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, the late fees come out \Nto exactly 1.58 million yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.49,0:21:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what happened? You look so pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I settled things so \NI pay him back for the tapes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In installments.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:29.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Right around the time \Nwhen Hayate's debt increased...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:32.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,There were yet more people \Nhaving a miserable experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One child's ticket to Rio de Janeiro please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.26,0:21:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Rio de Janeiro in Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:44.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone unable to discern \Nwhen they are being lied to,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,it is difficult to survive \Nin our modern society.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:49.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But let's just say that as people, \Nit's best to have an honest attitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:51.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,so see you again next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:57.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Moshi boku no yume ga kimi no kokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:57.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If my dreams have taken your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:02.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kizutsuke-tetara
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:02.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And brought it pain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:08.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sono omoi wa itsuka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:08.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, that anguish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:11.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Boku ga morau yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:11.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take from you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:17.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Taisetsu na mono ni furue-nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:17.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While trembling over something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:23.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kakezuri-mawatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:23.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And madly dashing about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:29.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Seou itami ni hibi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:29.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The hurt I bore made the days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:33.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Muimi ni sugita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:33.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Go by emptily
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:39.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oikaketa mama de oikosare-tsuzuke
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:39.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just chasing and continually being overtaken
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.04,0:22:44.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tohou ni kureru kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.04,0:22:44.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A wind who's lost its bearing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:49.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi no doko ni furetara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:49.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of you should I touch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:55.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ii ka o sagashita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:55.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I sought it out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:23:00.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mamoritai yo kimi dake wa tsuyoku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:23:00.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You alone, I want to protect so much
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:05.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yokubou no wadachi kara touzakatte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:05.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting away from the rut of desire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:10.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Itsuka subete te ni ireru sore ga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:10.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, it will all be ours and that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:14.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi to boku no Proof
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:14.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is our proof, yours and mine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.03,0:23:25.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Namida mo zenbu azukeru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.03,0:23:25.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Even all my tears, I entrust to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:29.38,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sign: Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.31,0:23:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, you've settled into \Nyour role as a butler pretty nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having said that, \Nyou still need more training.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be singing, all carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To start with, let's do special training,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.16,0:23:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you're ready no matter \Nwhen some ancient supermen
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.33,0:23:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or diabolical supermen come attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Supermen original to the anime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.42,0:23:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know when the anime \Nversion of "Hayate the Combat Butler"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.37,0:23:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will get its own original \Nsupermen, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.17,0:23:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.42,0:24:00.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Hayate, I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:19.72,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.30,0:24:01.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what might that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:03.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you try these clothes on for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:07.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, no matter how you look at it, \Nthat's a sailor uniform, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.09,0:24:09.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nagi! And here I was \Nwondering what you were up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.38,0:24:10.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.62,0:24:13.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,This frilly outfit is sure \Nto look good on Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.82,0:24:15.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,NOOO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.26,0:24:17.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:19.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Going to Hell in Cat-Ear Mode".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.72,0:24:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to Hell in Cat-Ear Mode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.72,0:24:22.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,For the future of Earth, \NI am at your service, meow!
